{"tid":2175001,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"何君堯歡迎警方拘捕行動　形容正義或會遲來但不會缺席","createTime":"2020-08-26T08:47:49.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-26T23:51:02.000Z","uid":130626,"like":3,"dislike":58,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"d95780299081fa84b73ffc910d8aaa3339b758af","tid":2175001,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-26T08:47:49.000Z","msg":"民主黨林卓廷被警方拘捕，涉嫌在去年「7.21元朗站事件」中參與暴動。當日被拍攝到與白衣人握手的立法會議員何君堯表示，歡迎拘捕行動，形容正義或會遲來但不會缺席，警方是採取應有及符合大眾期望的行動。<br />\n<br />\n何君堯表示，不同意民主黨指稱事件反映「警政系統濫捕」，警方一直表明是依法辦事，嚴肅跟進。他又說，社會撕裂是源於「泛黑攬炒」行動，對民主黨的回應感到失望及憤怒，亦希望警方盡早將去年參加「泛黑攬炒」的人繩之於法。<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1545981-20200826.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1545981-20200826.htm&d=hjP0Q4X6c9sJGZoCRXhatq3e3GGuF%2FCnRpDBLK0zENU%3D&h=e0f63388\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1545981-20200826.htm&h=9044eb72\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1545981-20200826.htm</a>"},{"pid":"892342ecc67bbd1bcceddb23e937a77903358233","tid":2175001,"uid":370079,"like":13,"dislike":1,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-26T08:49:25.000Z","msg":"見到條柒頭都想嘔"},{"pid":"75ac251b430f079bc9b6108be5e5b6e03f7c06b7","tid":2175001,"uid":11719,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-26T09:03:29.000Z","msg":"面皮厚到去火星"},{"pid":"afcab76fc8874288b959fd3b26a04af15f562e8c","tid":2175001,"uid":245849,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-26T09:05:17.000Z","msg":"我覺得佢係警告緊黑警"},{"pid":"5d24d3ca675d105e6d30bab578e1043dbda72bd6","tid":2175001,"uid":257409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-08-26T09:05:21.000Z","msg":"毋忘初心，唔想比人串好嬲好嬲就幫手推行動post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n再全面開戰， 9月6日九龍大遊行之藍絲紅媒好驚<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2171732\" data-auto-link target=\"_bla